# 🧠 SUPER SHORT MEMORY VERSION (for exams)

👉 Just remember this flow:

* `@GetMapping("/")` → show form + data
* `@PostMapping("/save")` → save data
* `@GetMapping("/edit/{id}")` → load data
* `@GetMapping("/delete/{id}")` → delete data

